sqlcipher

Sources: https://github.com/sqlcipher/sqlcipher
Use last release.

# Prepare

Repack original tarball as
sqlcipher-3.4.x/sqlcipher_3.4.x.orig.tar.bz2

# Usage

Arch - use sqlcipher package from community repo

# ARM

Replace config.sub / config.guess with:

http://git.savannah.gnu.org/gitweb/?p=config.git;a=blob_plain;f=config.sub;hb=HEAD
http://git.savannah.gnu.org/gitweb/?p=config.git;a=blob_plain;f=config.guess;hb=HEAD
